{"tid":376562,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"執行遊戲出現net framework錯誤","createTime":"2017-08-27T05:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T06:10:38.000Z","uid":113906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab368974207ff75efa7c9d17b077bf6e9445925f","tid":376562,"uid":113906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:51:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/134453_f22c07497d504e73b177c2fc7d04ffd2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F134453_f22c07497d504e73b177c2fc7d04ffd2.png&h=5a11025d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/134748_19b3cb38e800900509c54fc8d3a37edd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F134748_19b3cb38e800900509c54fc8d3a37edd.png&h=611d9327&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/27/134805_ae9724aa3cf3e2004a06fe8a5b679093.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F27%2F134805_ae9724aa3cf3e2004a06fe8a5b679093.png&h=21c44e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n系統WIN7 X64，執行遊戲出現呢個錯誤，遊戲目錄係英文，根目錄放D drive，已經嘗試修復<br />\n<br />\nnet framework及google過各種方法都係解決唔到，請教各位巴打絲打可以點樣解決呢個問題? <br />\n<br />\n(最壞打算係重裝系統)"},{"pid":"49f900ec16ccb59906ce10f402555a64459beef2","tid":376562,"uid":75692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T05:58:58.000Z","msg":"linux"},{"pid":"ec116e69eb07843ed05f9cd11f532f078926963c","tid":376562,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:01:13.000Z","msg":"我覺得要洗機"},{"pid":"1248a5bdf5695d477e4ee3d66ebd9e7d955ec723","tid":376562,"uid":113906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T06:05:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>linux</blockquote><br />\nLINUX系統可以解決大部分問題?"},{"pid":